  "title": "Solar O&M Planning Officer - (No exp. Welcome!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>~ 5 days work week, Monday - Friday 9am - 6pm</strong></p>\n<p><strong>~ Location: Tanjong Pagar</strong></p>\n<p><strong>~ To support solar energy project team</strong></p>\n<p><strong>~ No experience is welcome to apply, on the job training is provided</strong></p>\n<p><strong>~ 6 months contract and convertible to permanent</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Our client is a solar energy solution provider in Singapore</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan the schedule and arrangement with project team and engineers</li>\n  <li>Follow up on the plan and execution for project and logistics</li>\n  <li>Prepare site operation schedule.</li>\n  <li>Prepare site PV system operation critical event or checks together with engineer.</li>\n  <li>Learn and grow with the planning teams together</li>\n  <li>Work with project team on site preliminary report</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree – Building Construction Management / All field of engineering</li>\n  <li>No experience is welcome to apply, on the job training is provided</li>\n</ul>\n<p>HOW TO APPLY:</p>\n<p>Interested applicants, please click on “Apply Now” or email to submit your resume.</p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Stafflink Services Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 04C4294</p>\n<p>EA Personnel: Jason Bong Wee Kiat</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg. No.: R23116067</p>",
